  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p><em>\"If my actions can save any of them… Then I've gotta do something\"</em></p><h5 id=\"-strong-benefit-strong-\"><strong>Benefit:</strong></h5><p>If there is someone in danger, you must save them. Twice per long rest, when you see an allied creature become bloodied, you gain 1 Will of Fire point. Additionally, once per long rest when you would see an allied creature fall to 0 hit points, your movement speed is doubled until the end of your next turn.</p><h5 id=\"-strong-negative-strong-\"><strong>Negative:</strong></h5><p>Your true strength only comes out when you must protect those precious to you. You start every session with 0 Will of Fire points.</p>",
